<plot>Bing and his friends, Bob, Carol and Pearl perform skits, music and lots of fun. Highlights include: Bing singing "Desiderata" &amp; "In My Own Lifetime". Pearl sings, "Here's That Rainy Day". Bing and Carol duet on "Saturday Morning Confusion". Pearl and Carol do "Little Things We Do Together". Bing and Bob croon out some of the "Road" movie songs. All join in for "You've Got Good Friends", "Side by Side" and "What Would We Do Without You?".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?071224</url></doc>
